Fixed point met base 10

getal: 10 
fractional bits : 1
== 10.0 << 1 (bitshift with base 10 means move decimal point 1 place to the right)
== fixed point stored value = 100

getal: 10.5
fractional bits : 1
== 10.5 << 1
== fixed point stored value = 105
== 

